ovements within 4 to 6 weeks.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>How do I use Elixara?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        Apply a few drops directly onto the scalp and gently massage for 1–2 minutes. Do not rinse.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>How long should I use it?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        For best results, we recommend using Elixara consistently for 90 to 150 days.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>Who is Elixara for?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        Elixara is suitable for both men and women experiencing thinning, weak, fragile, or shedding hair.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>Can I use it after pregnancy or during stressful periods?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        Yes. Elixara can be added to a hair care routine during post-partum shedding, stress-related hair fall, or seasonal changes.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>Is the formula natural?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        The formula is made with plant-based extracts, is vegan, silicone-free, and paraben-free.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>Is shipping free?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        Yes, we currently offer free shipping today.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"faq-item\">\n\n      <summary>Do you offer a guarantee?</summary>\n\n      <p>\n        Yes, every order is backed by our 30-Day Money Back Guarantee.\n      </p>\n\n    </details>\n\n  </div>\n\n</section>\n\n<style>\n\n.elixara-clean-box{\n  background:#FFFFFF;\n  border:1px solid rgba(2,153,66,.16);\n  border-radius:24px;\n  padding:18px;\n  margin-top:-28px;\n  margin-bottom:18px;\n  box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.05);\n}\n\n.elixara-top-trust{\n  display:grid;\n  grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);\n  gap:8px